Package com.github.suloginscene.algorithmhelper.core.binarysearchtree

Class BinarySearchTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,​V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.suloginscene.algorithmhelper.core.binarysearchtree.BinarySearchTree<K,​V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Key for node
    V - Value for node
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BSTProfiler
    public abstract class BinarySearchTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,​V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Core abstract class to extend, providing utility methods. It can be used for making default-bst or avl-tree. But it is not suitable for red-black-tree, because nil node is not supported.
